{"tid":1543191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"望到呢張圖，唔罷課嘅你究竟諗緊咩？","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:30:16.000Z","uid":90486,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d58f8ef952cd5104570d56207318f6587c8c4988","tid":1543191,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyVTHsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyVTHsH.jpg&h=4498c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺嶺大，有3個freshmen全身黑衫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跪求</span>大學生罷課。<br />\n<br />\n究竟唔罷嘅大學生諗緊咩？大牌到好似黑警、林奠咁，要人跪地求你？仲要唔係求你做咩，求你履行公民責任，喺add drop period罷課咋。<br />\n<br />\n你話唔上堂追唔上進度？唔好呃細路，而家係add drop period，啲科隨時drop得<br />\n你話無罷課集會活動？咁你咪自己搞、搵人一齊搞<br />\n你話罷課無撚用？做文宣又好、簽聯署又好、擺街站又好，你要做，一定有野可以做<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過3個月嘅抗爭，3隻眼、1000個義士被捕、無數人受傷，淨係換嚟1個訴求，你地罷課罷一日就收皮，你班撚樣有無尊嚴？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林奠當初真係無估錯，一開學啲大學生就上堂不了邊有人會再出嚟抗爭？</span><br />\n<br />\n連幾乎無成本嘅add drop period罷課都唔做，咁不如咪撚爭取民主做港豬算啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學生，可唔可以比少少堅持？</span></span>"},{"pid":"077acdfa651f349adc131bd9b502fa2789bf3383","tid":1543191,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A